</P>
<P>
Ninety-seven Danish soldiers and scores of vehicles landed on
the Vlore port Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
With the new arrivals, the number of NATO troops in Albania for
humanitarin tasks has reached 5,300.
</P>
<P>
NATO has decided to deploy 8,000 soldiers in Albania to carry
out what it called the humanitarian "Allied Harbor" operation in
addition to several thousand troops for the military "Allied
