NICOSIA -- Italian Deputy Foreign Minister Umberto Ranieri said
here Wednesday that Italy supports Cyprus' accession to the
European Union (EU).
</P>
<P>
Ranieri made the remarks after a meeting with Geroge Vassiliou,
Cypriot chief negotiator in the EU accession talks.
</P>
<P>
He said Italy appreciates very much the efforts made by Cyprus
to meet the accession criteria. (BC-Cyprus-Italy) 
</P>
