<HEADLINE> Discussions on HK Cyberport Project to Proceed </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, April 29 (Xinhua) -- The Chief Executive in Council
has agreed that the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region (SAR)
Government should proceed with detailed discussions with the
Pacific Century Group (PCG) on the development of the Cyberport
based on the Letter of Intent signed with the Group.
</P>
