trusting partnership with Asean is an important part of China's
overall foreign policy. Since China became a full-dialogue partner
in Asean in 1996, their mutually beneficial cooperation in various
fields has been increased, and they have consulted and cooperated
with each other in both regional and international affairs.
</P>
