The Australian dollar finished in Sydney at 65.35 U.S. cents,
from Wednesday's close of 65.27 U.S. cents.
</P>
<P>
During the day it fell to a low of 65.26 U.S. cents.
</P>
<P>
"It was a reasonably quiet day for Aussie," Volanakis said.
</P>
<P>
At the close in Sydney, the Australian dollar was buying 0.6150
euro from 0.6106 euro Wednesday and 77.91 Japanese yen from 77.71
yen.  
