<TEXT>
<P>
COLOMBO, April 29 (Xinhua) -- Sri Lankan government troops
Wednesday killed 10 Tamil rebels in separate clashes with the
Liberation Tigers of Tamil Eelam (LTTE) in the north of the
country, a military spokesman announced here Thursday.
</P>
<P>
