philosopher Jean Baudrillard said that after coming out victorious
in its rivalries with the Soviet Union in ideological terms and
Japan in economic terms, the United States is now trying to divide
Europe by luring it into a trap of war which it does not want. The
United States is "coming to the rescue" of all the minority groups
in Europe like Muslims in Bosnia and Kosovo and Kurds in Iraq, who
actually have nothing to do with America.
</P>
<P>
