<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, April 29 (Xinhua) -- Visiting Israeli President Ezer
Weizman promised here Thursday to create a business-friendly
environment in his country by making peace with the neighboring
nations.
</P>
<P>
Speaking to more than 100 Israeli as well as local businessmen
at a breakfast meeting, Weizman, who arrived in Hong Kong
Wednesday, said a peaceful situation was very important for the
development of business.
</P>
<P>
