governments, whoever is elected, will do their utmost to quiet
down the area and live in peace with our neighbors because there
is no future if there were fighting," the president stressed.
</P>
<P>
He also stressed the importance of cooperation between
different countries and regions. "Life today is cooperation,
people should know each other, learn from each other and share the
common knowledge and the common aim," he said.
</P>
<P>
Weizman hoped that good cooperative relations can be
established between business communities of Israel and Hong Kong.
"I hope you would get along with our crowd here who are from
various fields of industries and commerce," he told Hong Kong
businessmen at the meeting. 
