<HEADLINE> "Spring City" Ready for World Horticultural Show (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Meanwhile, more than 250 hotels, guesthouses and recreational
centers have been mobilized to cope with the anticipated big
influx of domestic and foreign tourists. Now the city can
accommodate some 50,000 tourists every day.
</P>
<P>
More than 5,800 IC phones have been installed along every major
street, enabling users to communicate with 204 countries and
regions across the world. The Kunming telecom departments have
invested over 800 million yuan (about 100 million US dollar) on
improving the local mobile phone network.
</P>
<P>
"Our company has just bought 300 luxury public transit buses
and they are ready to shuttle between the city proper and the
exhibition venue," said Shang Hua from the Kunming City Public
Transit Company.
</P>
<P>
Many Kunming citizens viewed the horticultural show as a golden
business opportunity. Almost all stalls selling color films in the
city have reported sharp rises in their sales volume.
</P>
<P>
