<HEADLINE> Russia, S.Africa Emphasize Political Solution to Kosovo Crisis </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MOSCOW, April 28 (Xinhua) -- Both Russia and South Africa
Wednesday emphasized that the current Kosovo crisis should be
settled by political means.
</P>
<P>
At a news conference here, Russian Foreign Minister Igor Ivanov
noted that more countries, including NATO members, now stand for a
political solution, thus creating conditions for ending the crisis
"through joint efforts."
</P>
