<TEXT>
<P>
BELGRADE, April 28 (Xinhua) -- Two NATO planes crashed
Wednesday in Macedonia after being hit by Yugoslav anti-aircraft
fire, the official Tanjug news agency reported.
</P>
<P>
A NATO plane crashed in the western Macedonia after exploding
