<HEADLINE> Higgins to Meet Williams in Semis </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, April 28 (Xinhua) -- Defending champion John Higgins
advanced into the semifinal of the World Snooker Championships
with a 13-6 victory over Stephen Lee in Sheffield, England on
Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
